<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 14:06:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>支持和反以色列的示威者在洛杉矶放映哈马斯暴行镜头外发生冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/pro-anti-israel-demonstrators-clash-outside-l-a-screening-of-hamas-atrocity-footage/0000018b-b412-dea2-a9bf-f49e78140000</link><description>在宽容博物馆举行的放映是众多私人放映之一，旨在让舆论制造者了解哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击以色列边境社区的残酷程度</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 13:54:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/pro-anti-israel-demonstrators-clash-outside-l-a-screening-of-hamas-atrocity-footage/0000018b-b412-dea2-a9bf-f49e78140000</guid></item><item><title>一个更加军事化的以色列将是一个不那么繁荣的国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/a-more-militarized-israel-will-be-a-less-prosperous-one/0000018b-b449-dea2-a9bf-f4df86f50000</link><description>加沙战争大规模调动储备金对经济产生了深远影响。战后以色列将需要他们继续服役</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 13:49:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/a-more-militarized-israel-will-be-a-less-prosperous-one/0000018b-b449-dea2-a9bf-f4df86f50000</guid></item><item><title>新闻机构对以色列关于哈马斯大屠杀共谋的指控提出异议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/news-agencies-dispute-israeli-allegations-of-complicity-in-hamas-massacre/0000018b-b406-dea2-a9bf-f49e606b0000</link><description>亲以色列媒体监管机构的报道很快被以色列外交部采纳，声称新闻媒体“在 10 月 7 日大屠杀期间让记者与哈马斯恐怖分子混在一起”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 13:48:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/news-agencies-dispute-israeli-allegations-of-complicity-in-hamas-massacre/0000018b-b406-dea2-a9bf-f49e606b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人厌恶内塔尼亚胡。但对与巴勒斯坦人实现和平的绝望感更深</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israelis-loathe-netanyahu-but-despair-over-peace-with-palestinians-runs-even-deeper/0000018b-b3d1-d3c1-a39b-bff181c30000</link><description>随着内塔尼亚胡的支持率跌至历史低点，10月7日哈马斯袭击后的以色列民意调查显示，战后结束血腥的巴以冲突的希望更加黯淡</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 12:44:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israelis-loathe-netanyahu-but-despair-over-peace-with-palestinians-runs-even-deeper/0000018b-b3d1-d3c1-a39b-bff181c30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方解雇了拒绝与本·格维尔一起参加活动的安全志愿者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-remove-security-volunteer-for-refusing-to-attend-event-with-ben-gvir/0000018b-b3c8-dea2-a9bf-f3ded5cb0000</link><description>这位志愿者向《国土报》解释说：“我不会在拍完照片后就看到自己出现在本-格维尔的竞选活动中。”据他透露，警方一开始声称只有在与部长一起的仪式上才能向他发放枪支</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 12:37:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-remove-security-volunteer-for-refusing-to-attend-event-with-ben-gvir/0000018b-b3c8-dea2-a9bf-f3ded5cb0000</guid></item><item><title>德国人纪念水晶之夜，反犹太主义再次抬头</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-09/ty-article/germans-commemorate-kristallnacht-as-antisemitism-is-on-the-rise-again/0000018b-b3bd-df42-a78f-bfff79890000</link><description>柏林犹太社区卡哈尔·阿达斯·吉斯罗尔 (Kahal Adass Jisroel) 的经理上个月在犹太教堂遭到燃烧弹袭击时遭到袭击，他表示，德国在保护犹太人方面做得还不够。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 12:15:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-09/ty-article/germans-commemorate-kristallnacht-as-antisemitism-is-on-the-rise-again/0000018b-b3bd-df42-a78f-bfff79890000</guid></item><item><title>四名前阿拉伯裔以色列议员因反战抗议计划被警方拘留质询</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/four-former-arab-israeli-lawmakers-detained-for-questioning-over-plans-for-antiwar-protest/0000018b-b3b5-dedf-adab-f7b5c11e0000</link><description>高级阿拉伯监督委员会主席、前以色列议会成员穆罕默德·巴拉克首先受到讯问，随后三名前巴拉德党议员和该党总干事因涉嫌组织“可能导致煽动或损害公共和平”的集会而受到讯问。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 11:34:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/four-former-arab-israeli-lawmakers-detained-for-questioning-over-plans-for-antiwar-protest/0000018b-b3b5-dedf-adab-f7b5c11e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和哈马斯认为什么是加沙的“胜利”？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/what-would-israel-and-hamas-consider-a-win-in-gaza/0000018b-b365-dedf-adab-f7755a140000</link><description>对于以色列来说，此时此地消灭恐怖组织将被视为胜利。哈马斯希望维持永久的冲突状态，因此只要活着再战斗就将被其领导人视为胜利</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 11:25:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/what-would-israel-and-hamas-consider-a-win-in-gaza/0000018b-b365-dedf-adab-f7755a140000</guid></item><item><title>“完成工作”：在共和党总统辩论中，候选人竞相支持以色列对哈马斯的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/at-gop-presidential-debate-candidates-tell-netanyahu-to-finish-the-job/0000018b-b1f3-df42-a78f-bdf3fb760000</link><description>在共和党犹太联盟共同主办的辩论中，蒂姆·斯科特指责拜登双手沾满鲜血 ■ 罗恩·德桑蒂斯嘲笑“伊斯兰恐惧症” ■ 孤立主义者维韦克·拉马斯瓦米称乌克兰泽连斯基为“纳粹”，尼基·黑利为“穿高跟鞋的迪克·切尼”</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 11:24:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/at-gop-presidential-debate-candidates-tell-netanyahu-to-finish-the-job/0000018b-b1f3-df42-a78f-bdf3fb760000</guid></item><item><title>“我们 24/7 全天候运营”：保存以色列士兵精子的竞赛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-operate-24-7-the-race-to-preserve-israeli-soldiers-sperm/0000018b-af34-dea2-a9bf-ffbee1470000</link><description>在以色列与加沙哈马斯的战斗中，当局加大了对阵亡士兵精子利用的力度，并将道德问题留待以后处理。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 11:13:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-operate-24-7-the-race-to-preserve-israeli-soldiers-sperm/0000018b-af34-dea2-a9bf-ffbee1470000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队白天对约旦河西岸发动空袭，造成至少 10 名巴勒斯坦人死亡、20 人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-conduct-daytime-airstrike-in-west-bank-at-least-seven-palestinians-killed/0000018b-b397-dea2-a9bf-f39f87b80000</link><description>拉马拉巴勒斯坦卫生部报告称，共有八名巴勒斯坦人在西岸冲突和罢工中丧生；七个在杰宁难民营，两个在希伯伦和伯利恒附近</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 11:05:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-conduct-daytime-airstrike-in-west-bank-at-least-seven-palestinians-killed/0000018b-b397-dea2-a9bf-f39f87b80000</guid></item><item><title>拜登高级将领警告以色列长期加沙战争的风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/top-u-s-general-cautions-over-risks-in-a-long-gaza-war/0000018b-b398-df42-a78f-bfdb90eb0000</link><description>参谋长联席会议主席查尔斯·Q·布朗将军表示，以色列在加沙的军事行动的既定目标是彻底摧毁哈马斯，这是“一项相当大的命令”。他还表示，以色列国防军对其行为的公开解释还有改进的空间</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 10:27:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/top-u-s-general-cautions-over-risks-in-a-long-gaza-war/0000018b-b398-df42-a78f-bfdb90eb0000</guid></item><item><title>西方和阿拉伯官员齐聚巴黎讨论加沙援助；马克龙推动人道主义停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/western-arab-officials-talk-gaza-aid-in-paris-macron-pushes-for-humanitarian-ceasefire/0000018b-b343-d3c1-a39b-bfe370e30000</link><description>据估计，超过 150 万人（约占加沙人口的 70%）逃离家园，应对巴勒斯坦地区的危机大约需要 12 亿美元</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 10:11:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/western-arab-officials-talk-gaza-aid-in-paris-macron-pushes-for-humanitarian-ceasefire/0000018b-b343-d3c1-a39b-bfe370e30000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡谴责定居者的暴力行为，以此向拜登示好，然后急忙安抚他的支持者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-condemns-settler-violence-as-a-gesture-to-biden-then-rushes-to-appease-his-base/0000018b-b32a-dedf-adab-f73a764b0000</link><description>就在内塔尼亚胡在拜登的推动下谴责定居者的暴力行为几个小时后，他声称暴力行为来自定居点以外的“极少数”。拜登面临内部批评越来越多，美国加大对以色列施压，要求停火</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 09:51:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-condemns-settler-violence-as-a-gesture-to-biden-then-rushes-to-appease-his-base/0000018b-b32a-dedf-adab-f73a764b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的 TROPHY 系统如何保护部队免受加沙反坦克导弹的攻击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-trophy-system-anti-tank-missiles-in-gaza/0000018b-af67-dedf-adab-ef779df60000</link><description>哈马斯发布了许多视频，显示其部队向以色列军队发射反坦克导弹。在大多数情况下，它们实际上展示了以色列先进的拦截技术正在发挥作用</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 07:43:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-trophy-system-anti-tank-missiles-in-gaza/0000018b-af67-dedf-adab-ef779df60000</guid></item><item><title>五角大楼证实，美国袭击了叙利亚境内的伊朗目标；报告称九人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/u-s-strikes-iranian-targets-in-syria-pentagon-confirms-nine-killed-report-says/0000018b-b2ec-df42-a78f-bfef446c0000</link><description>美国国防部长表示，这次精确自卫打击是对伊斯兰革命卫队-圣城军附属机构对驻伊拉克和叙利亚的美国人员发动的一系列袭击的回应。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 07:32:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/u-s-strikes-iranian-targets-in-syria-pentagon-confirms-nine-killed-report-says/0000018b-b2ec-df42-a78f-bfef446c0000</guid></item><item><title>如果以色列不为加沙地带提供人道主义解决方案，埃及将</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/if-israel-doesnt-provide-a-humanitarian-solution-in-the-gaza-strip-egypt-will/0000018b-b0c1-dea2-a9bf-f0df18630000</link><description>阿拉伯国家向埃及施压要求开放拉法边境，美国强调人道主义危机，埃及可能决定在未经以色列同意的情况下开放过境点</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 06:54:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/if-israel-doesnt-provide-a-humanitarian-solution-in-the-gaza-strip-egypt-will/0000018b-b0c1-dea2-a9bf-f0df18630000</guid></item><item><title>中央情报局和摩萨德负责人会见卡塔尔总理，讨论以色列与哈马斯停火、释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-live/two-israelis-injured-in-west-bank-shooting-attack-idf-announce-death-of-soldier-in-gaza/0000018b-b1e8-df42-a78f-bdeb46190000</link><description>以色列军队称，经过一夜的战斗，部队控制了加沙地带北部哈马斯据点 ■ 巴勒斯坦人称，以色列国防军在约旦河西岸的袭击至少造成七人死亡 ■ 约旦河西岸发生枪击事件，一男一女受伤 ■ 在共和党总统辩论中候选人告诉内塔尼亚胡“完成任务” ■ 自加沙入侵开始以来，39 名以色列士兵被杀； ■ 哈马斯大屠杀至少造成 1,300 人死亡，241 名人质在加沙被扣，40 人下落不明 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部：超过 10,500 人死亡</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 04:33:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-live/two-israelis-injured-in-west-bank-shooting-attack-idf-announce-death-of-soldier-in-gaza/0000018b-b1e8-df42-a78f-bdeb46190000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的决定性战争举措：征服加沙城，迫使居民南下</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-tiebreaking-move-in-gaza-driving-its-residents-south/0000018b-b05c-df42-a78f-bd5fe5e40000</link><description>军方的新闻发布会和总理的讲话掩盖了更广泛的情况：征服加沙北部，驱逐居民，摧毁他们的家园。在下一阶段，这些可怕的图片将迫使世界寻找其他人来取代哈马斯</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-tiebreaking-move-in-gaza-driving-its-residents-south/0000018b-b05c-df42-a78f-bd5fe5e40000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列军队挺进加沙城，国际时钟正在滴答作响</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/as-israeli-troops-push-into-gaza-city-the-international-clock-is-ticking/0000018b-b089-df42-a78f-bdcb20530000</link><description>以色列认为哈马斯了解当地的力量平衡，并在现阶段选择狙击以色列国防军，将大部分自己的部队留在地道中。埃及和卡塔尔消息人士周三表示，新协议已摆在桌面上，而以色列仍持怀疑态度。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/as-israeli-troops-push-into-gaza-city-the-international-clock-is-ticking/0000018b-b089-df42-a78f-bdcb20530000</guid></item></channel></rss>